metadata.title: Music of the Maidu Indians of California
metadata.description: A collection of Maidu songs recorded by Frances Densmore from performances by Pablo Sylvers and Amanda Wilson in 1937. These songs were published in Densmore's *Music of the Maidu Indians of California* in 1958 and encoded by Daniel and Eva Shanahan.

issues.title: Publication preview urls are wrong
issues.description: HathiTrust uses a 'page scan sequence' number in the url. We  compute this by adding some number to the page number, but  it seems that this doesn't always work... Is there another query param that we can use to select the page?

songs.title: Song of the Duck Dance (c)
songs.lyrics_translation: The first flowers are blooming, so we are glad.

songs.title: Song of the Duck Dance (d)
songs.lyrics_translation: Lively, lively. We are lots of people.

songs.title: Circle Dance Song (a)
songs.lyrics_translation: There is a cloud in the heavens.

songs.title: Song of a Jumping Dance
songs.lyrics_translation: I jump down and dance, then I jump back up and dance.

songs.title: Song of the Two Boys Who Went for Clover
Look at the Poppy Flowers, Growing Fine
The Two Girls on the Bridge
songs.lyrics_translation: Put the two girls on the bridge so the crow cannot get them.

songs.title: Closing Song of the Adolescence Ceremony
songs.lyrics_translation: This is the last song. Some day we will sing it for another girl.

songs.title: The Neglected Wife Goes Away
songs.lyrics_translation: I am a fine-looking woman; still I am running with my tears.

songs.title: The Neglected Wife Is Pursued by Her Husband
songs.lyrics_translation: Wait for your property, you two. Wait for your property.

songs.title: The Gray Squirrels and the Fire
songs.lyrics_translation: We come after the fire to put it out.

songs.title: Song of a Hunter
songs.lyrics_translation: We have been hunting today. We are loaded down. The feathers are heavy.

songs.title: A Rabbit Is Going North
songs.lyrics_translation: I am hopping along. I am going north. I will get there after a while.

songs.title: A Goose Laments His Lost Brother
songs.lyrics_translation: How about it? My brother died. How about it? My brother died.

songs.title: Lullaby
songs.lyrics_translation: The swallow (to'lip) is singing for the baby.
